southern rata
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i> M. umbellata </i> also called ironwood the South Island variety of this tree. See rata.  (formerly <i>M.lucida</i>), rata, ironwood  (distinct from <i> M. robusta</i>)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka ironwood
